title: What does encantado de conocerle mean in English? - Answers
snippet: Apr 26, 2024 路 What does encantado de conocerlo mean? "Encantado de conocerlo" is a Spanish phrase that translates to "Nice to meet you" in English.

title: How do you Respond to encantada in Spanish? - Answers
snippet: Aug 30, 2023 路 Encantada literally means "Enchanted", but is used by women as "Nice to meet you." You could respond by saying "Mucho gusto", or "Igualmente".
